caption.title: Kinetics of replication by TCID 50 and the HA assay of 2016–2017win, 2017sum and 2014 H3N2 viruses at 33C, 35, 37, and 39 °C.
caption.p: a– d The kinetics of replication of the 2016–2017win, 2017sum and 2014 H3N2 viruses at different temperatures were determined according to TCID 50. e Influenza virus replication in MDCK cells at different temperatures was examined by the hemagglutinin assay at 96 hpi. The P-values were statistically analyzed by paired t test. * P < 0.05
